的是，由于签证要求，申请者需通过昆士兰商业技术学院授权的中介机构进行申请，机构列表见外部链接。</p><p><strong>联系方式</strong></p><p>格蕾瓦斯特山校区：</p><p>QIBT at Griffith University, 176 Messines Ridge Road Level 5, International Building M14</p><p>Mt Gravatt 4122 QLD</p><p>Telephone: (617) 3735 6900</p><p>Facsimile: (617) 3735 6901</p><p>qibt@navitas.com</p><p>黄金海岸校区：</p><p>QIBT at Griffith University, Parklands Drive Level 4, International Building G52</p><p>Southport 4222 QLD</p><p>Telephone: (617) 5552 8500</p><p>Facsimile: (617) 5552 8555</p><p>qibt@navitas.com</p><p>外部链接：</p><p>预科课程在线申请入口1：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=MrO2caJMwr-KeqJFZZZZZMuXbjNM5jAO1bjiSc7l8vX0i8C0lanEnl_E7gxamYRZJdBZjRe5nrXMa1OmQ9bpGAEcGhscJ-F8xjHc4Sv5rjOjqZ3k4AlZuaVs23gESFz1O2VsUR7kS-5rJTEbvOwvvqFzFIq1qrKDu1PKtmBAl0uo' target='_blank'>Apply online</a></p><p>预科课程在线申请入口2：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=qrTydPtGwx30hzWLSSSSSSQyVJWYV2HO7Fm_mYCYTd5_LUhnPaC3TJqO4gqOpg9YPhU' target='_blank'>Apply Today</a></p><p>昆士兰商业技术学院授权的中介机构列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhlj_kZqpfBfCAAATzzpES6O4a6i_CMxtbFbtRfu-iv1FimisRPGyRP3ERo4yiE02TPG4F42w09k4ujVjB4fy89d4Pj2WR4Vy_9dMd4ABPExFd1oCoC3iVMoCZzqp51oCaZ3JrV2tbKBBtsnraHqCn1fravwSYkwuJjA12YyunQjHU3cEt_' target='_blank'>QIBT AUTHORISED REPRESENTATIVE LIST</a>(PDF)</p><p>寄宿家庭申请表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=nrIeztAYwPxI1LlEgggggUpEnr-2UrSjVq3neNiNeDe6W3Ct-aQUZUDnxqNJ2so02FKHxH7ZqKQHEyiY0T94iFyscsGilVkpG103wXMfJGs2QNEWEdd-Jc4_MNnococPTDNon046kS1IjJFA60nSUTQlRfUUlCc-KHFTNFxJYs2eaRQ8-YLAmYJCZ_FQMxVH5L4_fBoZyvI4SzFj8N_' target='_blank'>Application for Homestay Accommodation</a>(PDF)</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ir67yhZGLmpEbtyTP-CWSxrTOYIFTJ2qGhkpyiyOrCeX11WemrywolWJIp-YTWoSmuftC2upjtTdrM1Ig853VSPi7_ExNvh5pWQmdQjwY-9QX8xWq8b4VriuDh0M0WcQOo-O0UO5BBA-YKxyYBAfhXMyJxjZohElo8PlZoSm97AXMyvwDef-zDZgtsm_UO1NdaB7' target='_blank'>2015 Griffith International St