ref='http://www.qianmu.org/生物医学' target='_blank'>生物医学科学</a>、生物技术、<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/分子生物学' target='_blank'>分子生物学</a>、<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/遗传学' target='_blank'>遗传学</a>、植物科学，且GPA5.0以上（以7.0方式计算，相当于百分制GPA70%）；或已拥有临床微生物学研究生文凭课程，且GPA5.0以上，也可申请，并可申请转30个学分至此项目，也就是说可无需再修该项目一年级的选修课程。该项目在内森校区开设，要求申请者提前联系导师并撰写研究计划。*(2)</li>	<li>另外，格里菲斯大学还开设有临床微生物学研究生文凭（Graduate Diploma of Clinical Microbiology），该项目仅面向澳大利亚本土学生招生。*(3)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7pywRjyJ_-dGGGGG0rweEp6eKr_9QJDJ6VW7ylRJXfRtRfDmylRok8R9NHR9k8xoB0xoXRgLp0xopaWoNxnovIc9R1cikhcLSAsKBoxC5oGoph1iNUOc5DRLYUl2CyTjC9X8iyT4OfZDFJmxq9X8lH1JEjX4Oy74xnGROfxO5jsaCyq_EuXd52ZuG' target='_blank'>Graduate Diploma of Research Studies in Science</a> Griffith University</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Lr8sWS2ckzD3-bXYjjjjjGyVbZH3YZSB0PGzIiIlBFxOQNcdoSL8S8jsyCo-ibehGH6hY9a5NJTmNQVDk7SDJaT1KZEBKiLXmptiUCtVjrgkerq7M0AfTUl9BVdIFHjcCfj3lMo9Duzb_1VWc93yk9O5Dhdo_71T6Y1oMYZFt3aRn9RNczeGqdocaTSPXlbPy' target='_blank'>Master of Science</a> Griffith University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=JrvWrUczkc7SCD3EYC7i7j_tCYncnB0360FVGg_4PdPZXjhdTCkwya7JrxY4Y-e7SY3m3Czc9ab4UZuEs4R5iRkpv9P5e9P70De3yia_w8kZKvvWUruoN17iH3rRjbG_4eY4l0srXE8Y47gQooyNUruoN1742mgUz9zmrb3tqWXDAsJPEcdoPWEf_rcWUHWcmUF37atv02PMhcnBxuPCByLGlSrRmjqlTh9vzRfmj9E4Af' target='_blank'>Graduate Diploma of Clinical Microbiology</a> Griffith University</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>化学</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:14.28%">			<p>QS世界排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.28%">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.86%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.86%">			<p>$21,920</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.86%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:17.86%">			<p>1月中旬</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:14.28%">			<p><a href='http://ww